{"tid":2016263,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人覺得流沙奶皇包好垃圾 ?","createTime":"2020-05-14T09:12:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-14T13:57:56.000Z","uid":225197,"like":8,"dislike":37,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"523305376964f9f90772e6c79a9d9d8615c6d324","tid":2016263,"uid":225197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T09:12:35.000Z","msg":"講緊酒樓即叫即蒸既流沙奶皇包<br />\n岩岩蒸起，諗住襯熱食果陣<br />\n一咬落去，啲漿就會辣親個咀，根本冇可能襯熱食<br />\n諗住等佢攤凍先食<br />\n一咬個包，塊皮又硬，個包又凍，入面啲漿仲瓊埋，成pat野咁<br />\n以前普通奶皇包明明好食過流沙既好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但而家間間酒樓都剩係識跟風做流沙奶皇包<br />\n究竟係邊條撚樣發明流沙奶皇包咁on9既野出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c513b56e5a006d8a1424f162be2d90352ca9f41","tid":2016263,"uid":321977,"like":19,"dislike":2,"score":17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T09:14:27.000Z","msg":"你個咀垃圾啲<br />\n我食又唔見有事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb2a13ab7b09f17d5d0285fdd7266b994fe76207","tid":2016263,"uid":225197,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"9c513b56e5a006d8a1424f162be2d90352ca9f41","tid":2016263,"uid":321977,"like":19,"dislike":2,"score":17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T09:14:27.000Z","msg":"你個咀垃圾啲<br />\n我食又唔見有事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T09:16:33.000Z","msg":"唔夠熱就會咁，有冇叫佢換過比你？"},{"pid":"c78b4127a38e139672a02e9cc9fe896589b62529","tid":2016263,"uid":225197,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T09:25:01.000Z","msg":"連登仔冇人鐘意食普通奶皇包？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae17068b82320426a2315ebde10be028ec3ce46e","tid":2016263,"uid":54528,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T09:28:53.000Z","msg":"細蚊仔先會食奶黃包"},{"pid":"c23842c0cc0ea487b1ee9d2b579691924d123a88","tid":2016263,"uid":225197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":